    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.08)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.24 + v2 + 0.40)) * v2)
    v1 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.73 * v0 + 0.17) * (v0 + 0.34 / v2 + 0.34)))
